[SPEAKER_01] Tu moraš početi iz nule,

537
00:44:20,639 --> 00:44:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] moraš griješiti,

538
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, ali ne možu ja griješiti.

539
00:44:23,199 --> 00:44:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ako čim prva griješku napravim,

540
00:44:24,960 --> 00:44:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] ne treba meni poslodavac reći,

541
00:44:26,519 --> 00:44:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] ok, nema problema, nastavi.

542
00:44:27,800 --> 00:44:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam gotov.

543
00:44:28,639 --> 00:44:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne mogu griješku napraviti.

544
00:44:30,440 --> 00:44:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja neću niti dopustiti.

545
00:44:31,880 --> 00:44:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja čim osjetim,

546
00:44:32,760 --> 00:44:36,300
[SPEAKER_01] moji senzori kad osjete da ja tu neću biti u tom prostoru 5.0,

547
00:44:36,300 --> 00:44:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] neću niti ulaziti u njega.

548
00:44:37,860 --> 00:44:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bolje se je povlačiti i raditi nešto.

549
00:44:40,039 --> 00:44:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam šta, ali neću riskirat da uđem u prostoru kojem nisam najbolji.

550
00:44:50,820 --> 00:44:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] I vijeme je za mali predah.

551
00:44:53,360 --> 00:44:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Upadamo uzre teme, znam,

552
00:44:55,079 --> 00:44:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali trebamo mali predah.

553
00:44:57,840 --> 00:44:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] To nam valjda nećete zamjeriti.

554
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] Plazma donosi rubriku Grickaj i Biraj,

555
00:45:03,219 --> 00:45:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo par teških pitanja postaviti našoj Ireni.

556
00:45:06,300 --> 00:45:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zaključan u sobi 12 sati

557
00:45:08,260 --> 00:45:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili zaključan u WC-u s mobitelom?

558
00:45:10,380 --> 00:45:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] U sobi 12 sati.

559
00:45:12,559 --> 00:45:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ipak bez mobitela.

560
00:45:13,940 --> 00:45:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] Bez mobitela, apsolutno.

561
00:45:15,599 --> 00:45:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] To mi bi baš bila želja.

562
00:45:16,840 --> 00:45:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono.

563
00:45:18,019 --> 00:45:19,639
[SPEAKER_01] I još bolje,

564
00:45:20,079 --> 00:45:22,860
[SPEAKER_01] zatvoren u šumskoj koli bi negdje daleko od svijeta.

565
00:45:22,860 --> 00:45:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] 24 sata bez mobitela, bez ničega.

566
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi je nekoga da me to odvede.

567
00:45:27,139 --> 00:45:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nova ljubav svaki mjesec ili jedna tri godine u tim godinama?

568
00:45:30,940 --> 00:45:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, glavam svoje iskustvo života jedna ljubav i jedna prava ljubav je zasi dovoljna.

569
00:45:35,719 --> 00:45:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] A dobro, ali u timedjerskim godinama?

570
00:45:37,219 --> 00:45:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] U timedjerskim godinama.

571
00:45:38,300 --> 00:45:40,619
[SPEAKER_01] Za ozbiljno ili onako malo šarat?

572
00:45:42,780 --> 00:45:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] A u timedjerskim godinama?

573
00:45:44,639 --> 00:45:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] A jedna ljubav je jedna ljubav, snaš?

574
00:45:46,519 --> 00:45:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna prava ljubav.

575
00:45:47,800 --> 00:45:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ja čim ti osjetiš pravu ljubav, bo boli gleda je u timedjerskim godinama jako lijepo da ti neko baš lijepo voli.

576
00:45:53,559 --> 00:45:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] TikTok ples u hodniku ili filozofski imunolog u ponoć?

577
00:45:57,719 --> 00:45:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] O, filozofski bolje zvuči.

578
00:45:59,480 --> 00:46:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, jo, ja bih samo plesala.

579
00:46:01,519 --> 00:46:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam ja neki ples, ja volim više izotraživati, proučavati, pratiti.

580
00:46:05,739 --> 00:46:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se vidim više u nekim tim, ono, ne znam, nisam neki plesni tip.

581
00:46:10,860 --> 00:46:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] Objasni posto ti put ili pusti da shvati kad zaboli?

582
00:46:15,280 --> 00:46:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pusti da shvati kad zaboli.

583
00:46:17,599 --> 00:46:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] A prešutiti jer si umorna ili razgovarati jer znaš da trebaš?

584
00:46:21,239 --> 00:46:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Razgovarati jer znaš da trebaš.

585
00:46:22,900 --> 00:46:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerovati ili provjeriti za svaki slučaj?

586
00:46:24,739 --> 00:46:29,099
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerovati ili provjeriti uvijek za svaki slučaj.

587
00:46:29,099 --> 00:46:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pitati gdje ide ili samo pratiti lokaciju u tišini?

588
00:46:32,420 --> 00:46:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ako pitam tinejdžera gdje ide ili provjeriti lokaciju u tišini,

589
00:46:37,360 --> 00:46:39,099
[SPEAKER_01] pitati u svakom slučaju gdje ide.

590
00:46:39,099 --> 00:46:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad ga ne provjeravati.

591
00:46:40,480 --> 00:46:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] I ništa nećeš dobit s tim ako si ti sad kao roditelj njega je provjeravao

592
00:46:46,480 --> 00:46:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] i dobio, otkrio da je on slagao.

593
00:46:49,119 --> 00:46:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Šta dobiješ od toga ništa, ali ako ga pitaš,

594
00:46:52,239 --> 00:46:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] resiran si za njegov život.

595
00:46:53,519 --> 00:46:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Prisjetiti se sebe u tim godinama ili praviti se da ti se to ne je dogodilo?

596
00:46:57,420 --> 00:47:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek se sjećati sebe.

597
00:47:00,840 --> 00:47:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sve je povezano.

598
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što ti, sve što se događa tvojom tinejdžeru,

599
00:47:04,260 --> 00:47:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] povezano je sa tvojom.

600
00:47:05,280 --> 00:47:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, sve što se događa njemu, što tebi smeta,

601
00:47:08,039 --> 00:47:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] je povezano sa tvojim nekakvim.

602
00:47:10,280 --> 00:47:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

603
00:47:11,219 --> 00:47:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] Što se tebi događalo.

604
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] Voljeti bezuvjetno ili ima išta ili?

605
00:47:17,500 --> 00:47:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] Bezuvjetno voljeti svoje djete,

606
00:47:19,699 --> 00:47:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači voljeti ga takav kakav je, kakav god da je.

607
00:47:25,400 --> 00:47:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ne voliš ga zato što je on nešto što bi ti htio da ono bude,

608
00:47:28,480 --> 00:47:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] što mi obično radimo, već ga bezuvjetno voliš.

609
00:47:31,780 --> 00:47:34,559
[SPEAKER_01] I kad je pogrešno, i kad radi, i kad te slaže,

610
00:47:34,559 --> 00:47:36,860
[SPEAKER_01] i kad ti napravi nešto, ti jednostavno pokažeš mu

611
00:47:36,860 --> 00:47:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] da uvijek postoji taj osjećaj.

612
00:47:38,480 --> 00:47:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] Prihvaćam te i volim te, takav kakav jesi.

613
00:47:40,840 --> 00:47:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tinejdžerstvo je baš što godine,

614
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] su te testiranja grešaka.

615
00:47:48,760 --> 00:47:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

616
00:47:49,280 --> 00:47:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jako je važno kako onda u tim situacijama reagiramo,

617
00:47:52,079 --> 00:47:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] jer baš to će kasnije isplivati kao u tim ljudima

618
00:47:55,840 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] u odrasloj dobi, koliko su bili podržani, prihvaćeni,

619
00:48:01,239 --> 00:48:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] koliko su njihove emocije viđene,

620
00:48:04,659 --> 00:48:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali u tome bez nekog možda posramljivanja,

621
00:48:07,719 --> 00:48:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] bez kritike, ali s druge strane uz tu korekciju ponašanja,

622
00:48:12,599 --> 00:48:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] da tako kažem.

623
00:48:13,539 --> 00:48:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Što kažete na to?

624
00:48:16,019 --> 00:48:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se postaviti u jednoj takvoj situaciji

625
00:48:18,219 --> 00:48:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] kad je djete pogriješilo,

626
00:48:19,440 --> 00:48:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] ako uzmemo pod pretpostavku da ti je to došlo

627
00:48:22,179 --> 00:48:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] i reklo što je ono veliki plus?

628
00:48:24,699 --> 00:48:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ako je djete pogriješilo i došlo je i traži tvoj savjet,

629
00:48:30,699 --> 00:48:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] možeš zato ovako jednu kavu

630
00:48:33,159 --> 00:48:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] i ćemo reći keks

631
00:48:36,119 --> 00:48:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] i lijepo popiti kavu

632
00:48:38,619 --> 00:48:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] i reći...

633
00:48:41,179 --> 00:48:42,559
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala što si rekao, a?

634
00:48:42,559 --> 00:48:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] Baš lijepo.

635
00:48:44,500 --> 00:48:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ništa drugo, jer ako si napravila,

636
00:48:46,420 --> 00:48:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] si vrkumski posao,

637
00:48:47,599 --> 00:48:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] ako je tvoj djete tebi došlo i je reklo,

638
00:48:50,119 --> 00:48:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] mama,

639
00:48:50,500 --> 00:48:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] gle, ja sam stvarno napravila neko,

640
00:48:53,219 --> 00:48:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili ja sam napravila nešto što je ono loše,

641
00:48:57,639 --> 00:48:58,760
[SPEAKER_01] možeš reći okej,

642
00:48:58,760 --> 00:49:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] jel misliš da ja nisam nikad napravila nešto što je loše?

643
00:49:01,260 --> 00:49:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš biti ljudski čovjek i sebe probuditi autentičnost,

644
00:49:05,440 --> 00:49:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] to oni trebaju,

645
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:07,780
[SPEAKER_01] jel ti misliš stvarno,

646
00:49:07,780 --> 00:49:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ja u tineđerskoj dobiju nisam to napravljala?

647
00:49:11,480 --> 00:49:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ti misliš stvarno,

648
00:49:12,400 --> 00:49:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] razumijem,

649
00:49:12,920 --> 00:49:13,480
[SPEAKER_01] ma reci mi,

650
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] možeš uvijek,

651
00:49:14,400 --> 00:49:17,639
[SPEAKER_01] znači tineđeri se odgajaju stvarno postavljanjem pitanja,

652
00:49:17,639 --> 00:49:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] gdje će oni jako puno razmišljati o sve,

653
00:49:19,599 --> 00:49:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] reci mi šta si mogao bolje,

654
00:49:21,400 --> 00:49:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] šta je bilo,

655
00:49:22,159 --> 00:49:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] kako je bilo,

656
00:49:22,739 --> 00:49:23,760
[SPEAKER_01] zašto ti se to dovolilo,

657
00:49:23,760 --> 00:49:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] kako ti se to dovolilo,

658
00:49:24,860 --> 00:49:25,440
[SPEAKER_01] ispričat mu,

659
00:49:25,440 --> 00:49:26,139
[SPEAKER_01] ja te razumijem,

660
00:49:26,139 --> 00:49:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] zato što stvarno ja sam isto to imala,

661
00:49:27,800 --> 00:49:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] sjeti se nečega,

662
00:49:29,219 --> 00:49:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] ma jesi garantiram nešto napravio loše,

663
00:49:31,480 --> 00:49:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] kad si bio tineđer,

664
00:49:32,559 --> 00:49:33,400
[SPEAKER_01] ispričaj,

665
00:49:33,480 --> 00:49:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] podijeli s njim i reci,

666
00:49:34,440 --> 00:49:34,719
[SPEAKER_01] plaš,

667
00:49:34,719 --> 00:49:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] šta je bilo,

668
00:49:35,219 --> 00:49:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] šta je mogao biti bolje,

669
00:49:36,699 --> 00:49:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je bila ta greška,

670
00:49:38,659 --> 00:49:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] šta ćeš sljedeći put kad se to dogodi,

671
00:49:40,380 --> 00:49:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćeš se ponašati sljedeći put,

672
00:49:42,179 --> 00:49:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] šta ćeš napraviti,

673
00:49:43,739 --> 00:49:44,920
[SPEAKER_01] ćeš opet upastiti u tvoj problem,

674
00:49:44,920 --> 00:49:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] viš kako je to,

675
00:49:45,619 --> 00:49:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] šta ti se to čini,

676
00:49:46,519 --> 00:49:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] kakav ti to osjećaj,

677
00:49:47,599 --> 00:49:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] eto to je to,

678
00:49:48,599 --> 00:49:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] i sjediš i piješ kalu za svojim tineđerom

679
00:49:50,780 --> 00:49:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] i pričaš o tome,

680
00:49:51,599 --> 00:49:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] i koučaš kako to je sad moderno,

681
00:49:54,039 --> 00:49:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] pitanjima,

682
00:49:54,980 --> 00:49:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] šta ćeš sljedeći put kad se to dogodi,

683
00:49:56,440 --> 00:49:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] da on sljedeći put već zna,

684
00:49:57,679 --> 00:49:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] ako ponovo upadnem u tu grešku,

685
00:49:59,659 --> 00:50:00,780
[SPEAKER_01] kako ću reagirati,

686
00:50:00,780 --> 00:50:01,659
[SPEAKER_01] neću više isto,

687
00:50:01,659 --> 00:50:02,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer ću pogriješiti,

688
00:50:02,940 --> 00:50:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] jer ću pogriješiti,

689
00:50:03,860 --> 00:50:05,360
[SPEAKER_01] želim pogriješiti,

690
00:50:05,360 --> 00:50:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] želim raz,

691
00:50:05,980 --> 00:50:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] želim mučiti iz toga,

692
00:50:07,059 --> 00:50:07,860
[SPEAKER_01] želim biti bolje,

693
00:50:07,860 --> 00:50:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer čim sam došao i rekao,

694
00:50:09,199 --> 00:50:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] svojim roditeljima da sam pogriješio,

695
00:50:11,039 --> 00:50:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači da sam svjestom da sam pogriješio,

696
00:50:13,619 --> 00:50:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] da bi ti ispravio nešto,

697
00:50:15,099 --> 00:50:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] ti moraš prvo biti svjestom da si pogriješio,

698
00:50:17,400 --> 00:50:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] i još plus kad to priznaš i kažeš,

699
00:50:19,380 --> 00:50:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači posao to,

700
00:50:20,619 --> 00:50:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] kad roditelji kojima to djeca kažu,

701
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno trebaju biti ono...

702
00:50:26,260 --> 00:50:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ponosni na sebe, ja.

703
00:50:27,480 --> 00:50:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] Bravo, ja.

704
00:50:28,599 --> 00:50:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] A ne ono šta?

705
00:50:30,760 --> 00:50:31,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

706
00:50:31,639 --> 00:50:32,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kako?

707
00:50:32,039 --> 00:50:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] I više ti nikad neće doći.

708
00:50:33,619 --> 00:50:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad neće, je, je, je.

709
00:50:34,480 --> 00:50:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] E, a ti je došlo,

710
00:50:35,440 --> 00:50:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] znači vjerujete.

711
00:50:36,559 --> 00:50:39,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ima s tobom emocionalnu povezanost.

712
00:50:39,239 --> 00:50:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] Stalo mu je od tvojeg mišljenja.

713
00:50:42,320 --> 00:50:45,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, znaš koliko si napravio dobar posao.

714
00:50:45,280 --> 00:50:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] I još jedno ću stvarno dodati,

715
00:50:46,840 --> 00:50:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer to vrijedi i za odrasle.

716
00:50:48,360 --> 00:50:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti nešto kaže o povjerenju,

717
00:50:50,159 --> 00:50:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] ne pričaj dalje.

718
00:50:51,400 --> 00:50:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] A ne sad.

719
00:50:52,659 --> 00:50:54,719
[SPEAKER_00] Sestro, moja tetka,

720
00:50:54,719 --> 00:50:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] vidi šta je bilo, šta su radili,

721
00:50:57,059 --> 00:50:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa na sva zvona.

722
00:50:58,300 --> 00:50:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

723
00:50:58,599 --> 00:50:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] I gotavo, gubiš povjerenje.

724
00:50:59,920 --> 00:51:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Gubiš povjerenje.

725
00:51:00,699 --> 00:51:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] Gubiš povjerenje, ne možeš ono,

726
00:51:02,340 --> 00:51:04,480
